ove more: Abu Jahl or Umar ibn al-Khattab.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cThe most beloved of the two was Umar.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3681 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/qiblah-salat-east-west\/","url_meta":{"origin":37235,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Qiblah: Prayer direction between two cardinal directions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhatever is between east and west is the direction of prayer.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"It has been narrated from more than one of the companions of the Prophet, that what is between east and west is the direction of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40382,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/05\/umar-faris-rum\/","url_meta":{"origin":37235,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Umar asks for the riches of Persia and Rome","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, call upon Allah to send abundance upon your nation, for the Persians and Romans enjoy abundance and have been given the world, yet they do not worship Allah as they recline on their couches!\u201d The Prophet, p